# Updated: 2026/03/07
# Description:
#   Git ignore rules for local runtime, secret, and generated artefacts.
# Notes:
#   - The state directory contains local-only data and must never be committed.
#   - Encrypted secrets still live under state/ by design, so they are also local-only.
# ################################################################

# Local runtime and secrets
state/

# Common editor and OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
*.swp
*.swo
